{"tid":365252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★Nowtv專訪 游b !!","createTime":"2017-08-19T05:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T15:14:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a88379d59fdbeead69ccd6a18b9b78fb441996ea","tid":365252,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=232778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D232778&d=bKLuNaTU6%2B3289Y0mkls9TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=1d5f4a92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D232778&h=9f7b9085\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=232778</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/134401_1fccaf71145cfd089b2562e1544ff544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F134401_1fccaf71145cfd089b2562e1544ff544.jpg&h=27e9beb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/134401_e2ab493e275914fdcae103f9f740495b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F134401_e2ab493e275914fdcae103f9f740495b.jpg&h=2db1ae3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】青年新政梁頌恆及游蕙禎立法會宣誓案風波，終審法院下周五會處理上訴許可申請。游蕙禎指已作終極敗訴的準備，梁頌恆就認為面對多方面的打擊，日後發展應「地下化」 。<br />\n<br />\n去年才晉身立法會，因為宣誓被取消議員資格，游蕙禎又要回到街頭。宣誓案有否機會終審，下周五就會有答案。經歷人大釋法及兩級法院的審訊，游蕙禎指作了終極敗訴的準備，但無論如何都不會在政壇消失，而梁頌恆就認為沒有做錯。<br />\n<br />\n2015年成立的青年新政主打延續雨傘運動的精神，目標要「議會革新」。同年區議會選舉已取得一席，鄺葆賢一擊即中，擊敗建制派對手。翌年再下一城，梁頌恆及游蕙禎在立法會選舉中當選，風頭一時無兩。但隨著宣誓風波，形勢大逆轉。<br />\n<br />\n有份創立青年新政的梁頌恆承認組織正處於迷失期，要思考如何重整旗鼓，但日後發展要「地下化」。<br />\n<br />\n至於官司後青年新政的前路包括會否派人參與補選等，梁頌恆及游蕙禎都希望得到終審法院的答案才決定。"},{"pid":"33daf8c8259f762e2aebdf57142cb42f4dfbc66b","tid":365252,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6b6cd902efa305fbbc3a1a714ffa828704b34d","tid":365252,"uid":17081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i999.photobucket.com/albums/af113/hydroxide6/Teddy%20boy/a2d80de7b783f727b93820f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi999.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Faf113%2Fhydroxide6%2FTeddy%2520boy%2Fa2d80de7b783f727b93820f5.jpg&h=2742e58d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fddc6db8010bd2bc0d174c9e17499699ab40d65","tid":365252,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0f550c8c8d4b23fd83b14dc89d9eb0c4e3f9ecf9","tid":365252,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/135737_a0595695956e76d783dbe65560fc7ffd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F135737_a0595695956e76d783dbe65560fc7ffd.jpg&h=7ca3b3e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3ac8a9a560422fbcdd1884de7dc90064ab05d40","tid":365252,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/19/135806_803631ede9c592af32a1521c29454337.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2F135806_803631ede9c592af32a1521c29454337.jpg&h=44f2b052&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c94434fdcfae8dc6f54be2661f7ec20c2b74df52","tid":365252,"uid":48442,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T05:59:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2aafd43e94d0fcdd1dc9cb3b4d9ee86e9f9970ee","tid":365252,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT